{"data": {"__GLOBAL": {"_ATTACH_BASE_VIEW": "img.nga.178.com/attachments"}, "__U": {"150058": {"uid": 150058, "username": "UID:150058", "credit": 135537154, "medal": "272,207,157,92", "reputation": "28_30,61_0,147_775,130_10", "groupid": -1, "memberid": 73, "avatar": null, "yz": 4, "site": null, "honor": null, "regdate": 1123989606, "mute_time": null, "postnum": 41083, "rvrc": 29, "money": 90765, "thisvisit": 1782044211, "signature": null, "nickname": null, "bit_data": 135537154}, "66989363": {"uid": 66989363, "username": "UID:66989363", "credit": 135275008, "medal": null, "reputation": "147_-300", "groupid": -1, "memberid": 39, "avatar": null, "yz": 4, "site": null, "honor": null, "regdate": 1762774156, "mute_time": null, "postnum": 2701, "rvrc": 10, "money": 0, "thisvisit": 1782082361, "signature": null, "nickname": null, "bit_data": 135275008}, "__GROUPS": {"73": ["学徒", 360672, 73], "39": ["学徒", 98528, 39]}, "__MEDALS": {"272": ["272.gif", "棒棒糖", "叔叔请你吃棒棒糖", 272], "207": ["207.gif", "爆竹声中旧岁除", "一支红杏出墙来", 207], "157": ["157.gif", "王者之剑", "王者之剑活动纪念", 157], "92": ["92.gif", "小心死亡之翼-", "2011年大灾变开服纪念", 92]}, "__REPUTATIONS": {"147": {"150058": 775, "66989363": -300, "0": "大时代"}}}, "__R": [{"pid": 872043535, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 50, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-17 16:02", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=872043204,45974302,7531]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=39728415]德国的野鸟[/uid] (2026-06-17 15:59):[/b]<br/><br/>哈哈哈，我以为你说的是你的金钼[/quote]<br/>一样啊 涨那么多不减你当我傻啊<br/>我不会去继续撬低位的么<br/>我的操作是滚动的。", "lou": 3320, "content_length": 73, "reply_to": 872043204, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781683334}, {"pid": 872108625, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 356, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-18 08:25", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "昨晚沃什讲话基本符合我的预判，应该说太符合了导致没有惊喜，所以市场也没有太大波动<br/>中间美股跳水是因为点阵图预测今年还会加息一次，但是更重要的是沃什说点阵图没用了，所以盘后大家又反应过来了<br/>那整体来说，议息会议就几条核心<br/>1   6.7，8月保证不加息，应该也不降低<br/>2   逐渐更改底层统计方式，为了让通胀降低， [del]你不是说通胀高么，我改了数据就没通胀了[/del]<br/>3   AI建设不会停止，允许市场自己筹钱，不会增加他们的融资负担<br/>4   接下来点阵图没有任何意义 所有基于之前的数据统计预判模型全部失效 <br/>5   缩表暂时不可能 但是改了数据统计之后是有可能。<br/><br/>那A股基本就会重新交易自己的逻辑<br/>通过吴总的发言得出结论，科技兴国不会改变<br/>但是<br/>需要更为缩圈，现在只是隔空喊话蹭概念的自己注意了，不要让上面用工具<br/>对应到操作里，那就是持仓最近小作文有，但是股价还没爆发的有中报预期的科技类。<br/>自己查一下 这几天有公告澄清自己没有某某业务的需要重点去分辨<br/>1 单纯澄清自己什么都没有---这种直接走人<br/>2 澄清自己没有某某业务，但是自己的原本的业务增速很大---这种可以留着观察 分辨上次上涨是不是因为被澄清的业务涨幅<br/>3 澄清自己虽然有这个业务，但是不占业绩太多占比----这种就看小作文轰到何时，一旦机构出场就走人。<br/>4 无澄清事项，并发布自己突破了某某工艺，进入某某领域，获得某某订单等----继续持仓等加速，但是验牌之前减仓", "lou": 3321, "content_length": 1113, "14": {"13": 1, "12": 2}, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781742312}, {"pid": 872109508, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 109, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-18 08:33", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "我已经发了 可能在审核", "lou": 3322, "content_length": 20, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781742815}, {"pid": 872111719, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 127, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-18 08:52", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "两融连续三天200多E的新增<br/>你们看出金日谁出金了？也就你们出金<br/>不过两融距离我之前预判的高点也蛮近了", "lou": 3323, "content_length": 94, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781743963}, {"pid": 872111951, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 120, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-18 08:54", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "我黄金今早已经开始分批进场了<br/>因为没有惊喜 也没有意外<br/>所以没有插针的位置<br/>现在我就是按我的技术策略慢慢增加多单", "lou": 3324, "content_length": 104, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781744080}, {"pid": 872117559, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 107, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-18 09:39", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "爽！！！！！！！！！！", "lou": 3325, "content_length": 22, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781746787}, {"pid": 872118481, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 48, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-18 09:46", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=872118387,45974302,7578]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=65329649]zippo578[/uid] (2026-06-18 09:45):[/b]<br/><br/>今天肯定不能希望黄线倒下<br/>这是增量来着[/quote]<br/>黄线昨天没新低就没反抽 你看今天新低了 反抽比昨天猛多了", "lou": 3326, "content_length": 57, "reply_to": 872118387, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781747201}, {"pid": 872122070, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 77, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-18 10:11", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "黄穿白了 今天非科技应该能获得一点喘息之机", "lou": 3327, "content_length": 40, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781748719}, {"pid": 872123255, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 69, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-18 10:19", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "移动电子完全达到之前计算器止盈位<br/>我剩利润开牌  其他没了", "lou": 3328, "content_length": 52, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781749182}, {"pid": 872124205, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 130, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-18 10:26", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=872123728,45974302,7587]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=65664557]维拉帕米不是米[/uid] (2026-06-18 10:22):[/b]<br/><br/>牛逼，yddz现在卖，没想到狼大会提一嘴[s:ac:晕][/quote]<br/>除非我忘记了 不然我长线一般进出会提一下<br/>要么就是我完全不想让你们知道我有这个票 那我就头尾都不说  等挣钱了给你们看我有多牛X", "lou": 3329, "content_length": 122, "reply_to": 872123728, "14": {"14": 1}, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781749578}, {"pid": 872124724, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 126, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-18 10:29", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "AIDC这块 我的思路没变 <br/>下半年行情 但是我买的票和你们的完全不一样 我的不在表里<br/>我是怕和你们撞车了 反正你们也不希望和我一辆车  各自安好", "lou": 3330, "content_length": 124, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781749784}, {"pid": 872125586, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 37, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-18 10:35", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=872125275,45974302,7591]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=66594393]江东jump[/uid] (2026-06-18 10:33):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大你的稀土板了，事到如今又要对不起的对象要加1了吗[/quote]<br/>我有啊 <br/>稀土现在涨的逻辑是  氧化镝和氧化乙<br/>我昨天还说了呢 你怎么会认为我没有？", "lou": 3331, "content_length": 77, "reply_to": 872125275, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781750118}, {"pid": 872126252, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 8192, "score": 41, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-18 10:39", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[img]./mon_202606/18/jmQ42-6rauKuT3cSvt-6d.jpg[/img]<br/>量化一点反应都没？消费咸鱼打挺都没见。。。", "lou": 3332, "content_length": 79, "attachs": [{"attachurl": "mon_202606/18/jmQ42-6rauKuT3cSvt-6d.jpg", "size": 30, "type": "img", "subid": 0, "url_utf8_org_name": "image%2epng", "dscp": "", "path": "mon_202606/18", "name": "jmQ42-6rauKuT3cSvt-6d.jpg", "ext": "jpg", "thumb": "120"}], "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781750376}, {"pid": 872126946, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 93, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-18 10:44", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=872126738,45974302,7594]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67138111]Altyport[/uid] (2026-06-18 10:42):[/b]<br/><br/>不要问狼大个股，狼大说了是 aidc 行情，不跟狼大同车不代表别的就不涨了。板块起来了一起飞。<br/>结合狼大之前说的，重点关注能拿到更多华为卡的 aidc 就完事了。[/quote]<br/>嗯 说的对<br/>我把能说的都说了", "lou": 3333, "content_length": 29, "reply_to": 872126738, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781750643}, {"pid": 872127693, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 148, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-18 10:49", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "无聊了  不懂黄线的喘息能不能支持一天<br/>不然呼吸窗口太小了<br/><br/>现在真是慢牛行情 金融负责慢 科技负责牛  <br/>这样还是蛮好的<br/><br/>顺便无聊吹水  下半年行情我都是提前很早和你们说了<br/>不管是半导体材料还是别的 基本都是领先市场给你们<br/>所以就不要等我的个股了  你们这里暂时还没有能体现出实力的。 <br/>你们要想获得更多 得有你们自己的能力展示  到时候我会找你的。", "lou": 3334, "content_length": 306, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781750949}, {"pid": 872128196, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 8192, "score": 62, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-18 10:52", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=872127497,45974302,7595]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=6313142]暮残[/uid] (2026-06-18 10:47):[/b]<br/><br/>紫金是这样的<br/>我之前也是紫金跟江铜二选一<br/>不选紫金的原因就是紫金里面全是T王散户，非强利好高开必砸你一波<br/>而且狼大说的，股票名字也很重要，买铜就买最纯的，江铜金也能吃到，弹性好[/quote]<br/><br/>[img]./mon_202606/18/jmQ43-bh73K6T1kS9u-1j.jpg[/img]<br/>你看 我就吃一天<br/>昨天拿来赌期货的<br/>我主要还是科技  这种就是玩玩 有得吃我就出去  不污染我的持仓。", "lou": 3335, "content_length": 128, "attachs": [{"attachurl": "mon_202606/18/jmQ43-bh73K6T1kS9u-1j.jpg", "size": 7, "type": "img", "subid": 0, "url_utf8_org_name": "image%2epng", "dscp": "", "path": "mon_202606/18", "name": "jmQ43-bh73K6T1kS9u-1j.jpg", "ext": "jpg", "thumb": "56"}], "reply_to": 872127497, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781751135}, {"pid": 872129658, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 83, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-18 11:02", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=872129370,45974302,7599]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=64648193]一生一股绊倒铁盒[/uid] (2026-06-18 11:00):[/b]<br/><br/>楼里有人懂白银吗，现阶段应该可以看着黄金做吧？理论上还有工业需求，但是目前的价格好像没有看见很大的影响，大多数时候跟金走[/quote]<br/>这波不要做白银 应该说未来不要做白银。", "lou": 3336, "content_length": 41, "reply_to": 872129370, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781751745}, {"pid": 872130468, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 259, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-18 11:08", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "昨天我朋友问我<br/>所有大消息落地了 科技要不要出场<br/>我回答他 <br/>最近会有震荡，你能不能接受你这几天没有那么赚钱<br/>他说可以<br/>然后反手送了我一辆车", "lou": 3337, "content_length": 126, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781752089}, {"pid": 872132892, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 63, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-18 11:23", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=872132600,45974302,7605]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=8618693]zq19871127[/uid] (2026-06-18 11:21):[/b]<br/><br/>额，不是我幸灾乐祸，但刚才外面看到个回复笑死我了，我是真没忍住。<br/><br/>有人发帖问红利低波怎么了，跌这么猛，<br/><br/>有人回复你这是买到绿利高波了，请补仓。[/quote]<br/>他们不是说么  跌才是好 越跌越补么<br/>你直接这么回他就行  看他补不补", "lou": 3338, "content_length": 63, "reply_to": 872132600, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781753013}, {"pid": 872135310, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 81, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-18 11:39", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=872133784,45974302,7607]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67144398]轩羽灬[/uid] (2026-06-18 11:29):[/b]<br/><br/>老登还是有点话语权的，。小心大家长下场[/quote]<br/>GJD都没筹码了 他有什么话语权<br/>你但凡看见GJD又偷偷买回老登 那就小心喊话降温科技  没有出现这种情况那没什么可以担心的。", "lou": 3339, "content_length": 115, "reply_to": 872133784, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781753958}], "__T": {"fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "topic_misc": null, "subject": "自立自强，科学技术打头阵", "locked": 0, "recommend": 0, "quote_to": null, "quote_from": 0, "type": 36, "replies": 155637, "authorid": 150058, "postdate": 1768179906, "lastpost": 1782111217, "jdata": null, "author": "-阿狼-", "lastposter": "子非鱼丶小窝", "digest": 0, "lastmodify": 1782111220, "tpid": 0, "post_misc_var": {"content_length": 412, "fid": 706, "comment_id": ",854270755,860174433", "14": {"17": 1, "14": 4, "13": 4, "12": 1}, "16": "63335896,19412700,26652007,67067074,20672033,66881586,67068843,66199622,60819388,60409766,67057614,60264977,61082281,42701832,66998841,61574956,61272875,67082978,66949654,65530601,60630412,60240136,66038632,63481990,61973100,60192597,669